  storyboardSlides:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 464835532f7234b7c872f0bd47aa8e30, type: 3}
    titleText: Into the Contamination
    bodyText: Entering the contaminated research wing, Astrid hunts for clues to
      Sydnell's location amid advanced mutants capable of running, jumping, and spitting
      poison
  winStoryboardSlides: []
  instructionPanel: {fileID: 309444210}
  instructionSlides:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 17f83c92ed1b9030394b9678ef8496a3, type: 3}
    bodyText: Decoy Launcher Unlocked  A Decoy Launcher has been added to your arsenal.
      Press [3] to equip it and [Left Click] to throw a decoy device. Enemies will
      be distracted and investigate the decoy location. Use it to create openings
      or split enemy groups apart.
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 5c0f4ef06a73d214cbeda2b8f19547bf, type: 3}
    bodyText: "Eliminate All Threats\n\nThe Bio-Lab is infested with Mutants and
      Scout Drones. Mutants deal heavy melee damage \u2014 keep moving and aim for
      the head. Scout Drones attack from range \u2014 take them out first. Clear
      all enemies to secure the area."
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c6cfe33daa1768bf89b808626b2956f7, type: 3}
    bodyText: 'Activate All Pressure Plates


      Four pressure plates are hidden
      across the Bio-Lab. Place heavy objects on each plate to activate them. Pick
      up heavy boxes with [E] and carry them to each plate. All four plates must
      be active simultaneously to unlock the next area.'
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aacdc9b525dff539aaa73a1ba0eb002e, type: 3}
    bodyText: 'Find the Access Key


      Once all pressure plates are active, the
      Evacuation Key will be accessible. Walk over it to collect it automatically.
      Head to the Exit Door and press [E] to proceed to the Reactor Chamber.'
  slideImage: {fileID: 1988329608}
  slideBodyText: {fileID: 129200728}
  slideCounterText: {fileID: 1726293379}
  slideNextButton: {fileID: 1905156798}
  slidePrevButton: {fileID: 73174483}
